data.description: In the highly desirable community of Liberty Hall Plantation, this 3BD/2.5 BT home has plenty of space to enjoy, with a little TLC! Upon walking in you will be greeted by a spacious foyer that leads to the formal dining area, an office, the garage or the half bath. The open floorplan is perfect for entertaining! The kitchen features stunning countertops with tons of cabinet space & a large pantry. Up the stairs you'll reach a spacious loft that includes a laundry room and additional closets. This spacious Master bedroom offers a large walk-in closet, a spacious Master bathroom with double vanity, garden tub & separate shower. The 2 generously sized bedrooms, shares a full hallway bath. The huge backyard is fully enclosed with a privacy fence and screened in patio.Seller to have the property deep cleaned and carpets professionally cleaned prior to closing.
